name: Swaying Eels in the Coral Reefs

imgDesc.text:
This sort of eel hides in the deep sea coral formations and is especially sensitive to musical melodies. When agitated by such, they will poke their heads out.
When <color=#ffe14b>all their heads are sticking out, Press to unleash a Pause Soundwave</color> and cause them to be unable to duck back into the coral, leaving them bopping to the melody constantly...
